statements: SELECT * FROM website_visitors;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_visitors WHERE id = 1;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM website_visitors WHERE page_visited = 'Homepage';
SELECT * FROM website_visitors ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, page_visited FROM website_visitors WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT * FROM website_visitors WHERE visitor_id = 1234 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT DISTINCT visitor_id FROM website_visitors WHERE page_visited LIKE '%home%' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(page_visited) AS total_visits FROM website_visitors GROUP BY visitor_id HAVING COUNT(page_visited) > 5 ORDER BY total_visits DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited, DATE(timestamp) AS visit_date FROM website_visitors WHERE visitor_id IN (5678, 7890) ORDER BY visit_date, visitor_id;

SELECT AVG(CAST(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM timestamp) AS INT)) AS avg_visit_duration FROM website_visitors WHERE page_visited = 'contact' GROUP BY visitor_id HAVING count(visitor_id) > 1 ORDER BY avg_visit_duration DESC;
